Package: opentenbase
Architecture: all
Depends:
 opentenbase-server (= ${binary:Version}),
 opentenbase-client (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: distributed SQL database (metapackage)
 OpenTenBase is an enterprise-level distributed SQL database management
 system based on PostgreSQL. It provides distributed transactions,
 horizontal scalability via sharding, and multi-tenant capabilities.
 .
 This is a convenience metapackage that depends on opentenbase-server
 and opentenbase-client for a typical single-node installation.

Package: opentenbase-server
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 opentenbase-client (= ${binary:Version}),
 adduser,
 lsb-base
Description: OpenTenBase server binaries (postgres, gtm, pg_ctl)
 OpenTenBase is an enterprise-level distributed SQL database management
 system based on PostgreSQL.
 .
 This package contains the server binaries (postgres, initdb, pg_ctl,
 gtm, gtm_proxy, initgtm, ...), private shared libraries, the
 opentenbase-ctl management script, and a systemd unit. It also
 creates the opentenbase system user and data directories.

Package: opentenbase-client
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenTenBase client utilities (psql, pg_dump)
 OpenTenBase is an enterprise-level distributed SQL database management
 system based on PostgreSQL.
 .
 This package contains the client utilities (psql, pg_dump, pg_dumpall,
 pg_restore, pg_basebackup, createdb, dropdb, createuser, dropuser).
 Wrappers are exposed under /usr/bin/ with an opentenbase- prefix to
 avoid conflicts with system PostgreSQL client packages.

Package: opentenbase-contrib
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 opentenbase-server (= ${binary:Version})
Description: OpenTenBase contributed extensions
 OpenTenBase is an enterprise-level distributed SQL database management
 system based on PostgreSQL.
 .
 This package contains contributed extensions (hstore, pg_stat_statements,
 postgres_fdw, pgcrypto, citext, etc.) and OpenTenBase-specific modules.

Package: libopentenbase-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 libssl-dev,
 libreadline-dev,
 zlib1g-dev
Description: Development headers and static libraries for OpenTenBase
 OpenTenBase is an enterprise-level distributed SQL database management
 system based on PostgreSQL.
 .
 This package contains the C header files and static libraries needed
 to build applications and extensions against OpenTenBase.

Package: opentenbase-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Documentation for OpenTenBase
 OpenTenBase is an enterprise-level distributed SQL database management
 system based on PostgreSQL.
 .
 This package contains README files, the project license, and
 example configurations.
